This is just a reference to resource Exec['sm-restart-lighttpd'], this resource is defined as following in sm.pp:

 908 define platform::sm::restart {
 909   exec {"sm-restart-${name}":
 910     command => "sm-restart-safe service ${name}",
 911   }
 912 }

So yes, the actually execution is sm-restart-safe.
